&lt;p&gt;绝对定位会随着页面滚动而移动,固定定位则不会.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.helloimg.com/images/2022/02/27/GV4IwK.png&#34; alt=&#34;20201220093438&#34; /&gt;
